                                                                                                            3.13.4e_ODP[1]     One or more of the following is/are selected: physical isolation
                                                                                                                               techniques; logical isolation techniques.
                                                                                                            3.13.4e_ODP[2]     Physical isolation techniques are defined. (If selected in
                                                                                                                               3.13.4e_ODP[1])
                                                                                                            3.13.4e_ODP[3]     Logical isolation techniques are defined. (If selected in
                                                                                                                               3.13.4e_ODP[1])
                                                                                                            3.13.4e[a]         <3.13.4e_ODP[2]: physical isolation techniques and/or 3.13.4e_ODP[3]
                                                                                                                               logical isolation techniques> are employed in organizational systems
                                                                                                                               and system components.
                                                                                                            POTENTIAL ASSESSMENT METHODS AND OBJECTS
